{"tid":512081,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"810場平費Sir紀錄 雲加：場場如俄羅斯輪盤","createTime":"2017-12-28T06:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T11:50:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"449e900cd11644f7eeac41dc95970d3d2fbf5fb4","tid":512081,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:38:22.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=4C7oGhvJJ%2Ff39LJdFoGvo%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9b223ff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴領隊雲加今日將追平前曼聯領隊費格遜創下的810場英超執教次數紀錄，他感觸良多，坦言21年來每場都令他膽戰心驚。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴在今日的英超快車將會作客水晶宮，將是領隊雲加（Arsene Wenger）執教的第810場英超比賽，將追平曼聯名帥費格遜的英超領軍次數紀錄。雲加賽前坦言從未想過自己能夠在英超領軍這麼久：「如果在我當年對布力般流浪那場比賽時，你們告訴我，我會執教810場英超的話，我一定會說你們是神經病。」雲加在1996年10月首場執教阿仙奴以2:0擊敗布力般流浪。<br />\n<br />\n雲加又表示不僅英超，他亦沒估計過自己會這麼長壽：「我還記得當我33歲時，我估計自己人生不會超過60歲，現在每一場比賽都像俄羅斯輪盤一樣，你永遠不會知道子彈會不會在下一輪便發射出來，所以我仍無法相信現在種種紀錄。」<br />\n<br />\n雲加坦言，過去21年英超起了不少變化，阿仙奴每季所受到的挑戰愈來愈嚴峻：「我已經在位21年，學會不再埋怨，現在曼城、曼聯和車路士的資源都比我們多，但我們要懂得接受現實，我認為我們仍可用自己的方式爭取成功。」<br />\n<br />\n近年不少阿仙奴球迷都認為雲加不再適合執教兵工廠，不過他表示仍不忘初衷：「我明白球迷不願意聽到我們的資源比不上其他球會，同時希望我們贏得每場比賽，我的工作是把球隊的實力發揮出來，最終目標是讓所有人都高興，雖然這不是經常能夠做到，但我從不放棄嘗試。」"},{"pid":"b89d7a76cfb88715850e4edf1609d2162037d622","tid":512081,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:38:36.000Z","msg":"Cloud add<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3f36dfcb9394e6ebfd2618ec4fa79e56f3028a","tid":512081,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:42:32.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79118c2dbfb7039fb38f70aeb406ca536fa2b88","tid":512081,"uid":76753,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"唔記得入子彈呀"},{"pid":"1cf75b9d64bdbdf45b920563b3782868f247c4df","tid":512081,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:45:04.000Z","msg":"雲加超越費蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2722495edb7ebbf05db555e2aba781090968a13","tid":512081,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b89d7a76cfb88715850e4edf1609d2162037d622","tid":512081,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:38:36.000Z","msg":"Cloud add<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"Yaya<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456c804917630629e5eae10a7cd5fa7f94a81532","tid":512081,"uid":11254,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"呢D記錄分分鐘永遠都無人破到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84b4ceaa5ae5c3c77930b61c7172679d80bc92b","tid":512081,"uid":21896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:51:36.000Z","msg":"好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bff558b48d00e06d30e1ef624a28f436e3fe1d","tid":512081,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"456c804917630629e5eae10a7cd5fa7f94a81532","tid":512081,"uid":11254,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"呢D記錄分分鐘永遠都無人破到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:51:39.000Z","msg":"只有雲加可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8e5db97c157985dc1bcb4c0ce6a2d5ab6c691d","tid":512081,"uid":70846,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"作為死阿妓，就算幾撚嬲雲膠啲排陣同埋啲死契仔，都係好撚唔捨得佢"},{"pid":"612f0ed83af4aad1562b4e3e0d812b2bb99ef17a","tid":512081,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"雲加今晚大炒水晶宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9c4b1f671ab7333cb751732a46cc2b699010